msgid ""
"Returns the sum of two Legendre series `c1` + `c2`.  The arguments are "
"sequences of coefficients ordered from lowest order term to highest, i.e., "
"[1,2,3] represents the series ``P_0 + 2*P_1 + 3*P_2``."
